.SH "NAME"
mc_reply_exception \- send an exception reponse
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.sp
*int mc_reply_exception(mc_t *\fIctx\fR, const uint8_t *\fIreq\fR, unsigned int \fIexception_code\fR);
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.sp
The \fImc_reply_exception()\fR function shall send an exception response based on the \fIexception_code\fR in argument\&.
.sp
